==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Littleness
<hw>Lit"tle*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality of being
little; <as>as, <ex>littleness</ex> of size, thought, duration, power,
etc.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Smallness; slightness; inconsiderableness;
narrowness; insignificance; meanness; penuriousness.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>littler</ent>⟦br⟧
